msgid "Display"
msgstr "显示屏"

#: ../../source/hardware/display.rst:8 c6c01b5a00ef49b3ac4216a3bb2cb5e0
msgid "A lcd display library"
msgstr "LCD 屏幕显示库"

#: ../../source/hardware/display.rst:15 d9e7e3e16d7e4460a7b83998e7e59176
msgid "M5 Series Display Libraries"
msgstr "M5 系列显示库说明"

#: ../../source/hardware/display.rst:18 f4cb7bbeeaa14f7b80a894c725301dbd
#, fuzzy
msgid "1. Display (M5.Lcd)"
msgstr "1. 显示"

#: ../../source/hardware/display.rst:19 1510b6c3572f414daa8f7d99ea9c95c8
msgid ""
"A low-level graphics library providing basic screen drawing, text, lines,"
" and color management."
msgstr "底层图形库，提供屏幕绘制、文字、线条、颜色管理等基础功能。"

#: ../../source/hardware/display.rst:20 e0a1b9b5312d4561bc567f64fd7490c2
msgid ""
"Can be used independently, suitable for scenarios that only require "
"drawing graphics or text."
msgstr "可独立使用，适合只需要绘制图形或文字的场景。"

#: ../../source/hardware/display.rst:21 7332cc75b9324610b2390afcfc0b497a
msgid ""
"**Access via**: ``M5.Lcd.fillRect()``, ``M5.Lcd.drawRect()``, "
"``M5.Lcd.drawString()``, etc."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/hardware/display.rst:24 dada5cb742f941d99902e3acb86c0e27
msgid "2. M5Widgets"
msgstr "2. M5Widgets"

#: ../../source/hardware/display.rst:25 ae79af932293473f897549133504b0bf
msgid ""
"A basic UI widget library providing labels, image displays, and other UI "
"controls."
msgstr "基础控件库，提供标签、图片显示等 UI 控件。"

#: ../../source/hardware/display.rst:26 8804bc37179442388f107e11ea02f247
msgid "Built on top of M5GFX."
msgstr "底层依赖 M5GFX。"

#: ../../source/hardware/display.rst:27 e6c97072aad449b5a3d644cd9e4902dc
msgid "Suitable for simple interactive UI elements."
msgstr "适合需要简单交互控件的界面。"

#: ../../source/hardware/display.rst:28 99a387b995a94c0784b51ccf3e472479
msgid ""
"**Access via**: ``M5.Widgets.Label()``, ``M5.Widgets.Image()``, "
"``M5.Widgets.Rectangle()``, etc."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/hardware/display.rst:29 30795aa1001a4d6da0e5cfbab1a2d597
msgid ""
"**Important**: ``M5.Widgets`` provides UI component **classes**, not "
"drawing methods."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/hardware/display.rst:32 6f680ecf616244238043b6d02968f344
msgid "3. M5UI"
msgstr "3. M5UI"

#: ../../source/hardware/display.rst:33 d4b4c0e01e674dd6b773ccc38006e4d3
msgid "A high-level UI framework based on LVGL."
msgstr "高层 UI 框架，基于 LVGL 封装。"

#: ../../source/hardware/display.rst:34 09c6124bcf1240c7b7287422b7c32be3
msgid ""
"Provides page management, multi-widget layouts, and unified event "
"handling."
msgstr "提供页面管理、多控件布局和统一事件处理。"

#: ../../source/hardware/display.rst:37 5717a7e5c3864f4bac4b0de30f7d4606
msgid "Usage Tips"
msgstr "使用提示"

#: ../../source/hardware/display.rst:38 e08c4d185c134335a11031e8bf84279f
msgid ""
"⚠️ Do not mix M5GFX, M5Widgets, and M5UI simultaneously, as it may cause "
"rendering issues or event conflicts."
msgstr "⚠️ 不建议同时混用 M5GFX、M5Widgets、M5UI，可能导致渲染异常或事件冲突。"

#: ../../source/hardware/display.rst:39 6f5d53f62a1b48dc884cccab6650b6cd
msgid "For graphics-only drawing → use M5GFX."
msgstr "单独绘图 → 使用 M5GFX。"

#: ../../source/hardware/display.rst:40 aec031e8fd08413c9632c315597466ab
msgid "For simple interactive widgets → use M5Widgets."
msgstr "简单控件交互 → 使用 M5Widgets。"

#: ../../source/hardware/display.rst:41 3d4e32575bf54d5b910c10c1fdeed414
msgid "For multi-page UI → use M5UI."
msgstr "多页面 UI → 使用 M5UI。"

#: ../../source/hardware/display.rst:44 ced466629678499d928efd1bf0f71ea1
msgid "Common Mistakes to Avoid"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/hardware/display.rst:45 fe13c95e680a4c9f94c461c7a289a4e0
msgid ""
"❌ **WRONG**: ``Widgets.fillRect()`` or ``Widgets.drawRect()`` - These "
"methods do not exist in Widgets module"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/hardware/display.rst:46 f0c75df256fc439a979b68f085653a9c
msgid ""
"✅ **CORRECT**: ``M5.Lcd.fillRect()`` or ``M5.Lcd.drawRect()`` - Use "
"M5.Lcd for drawing methods"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/hardware/display.rst:47 aabd2eb428e44e86838e2ee030c125a4
msgid ""
"❌ **WRONG**: ``from M5 import Widgets; Widgets.fillRect(...)`` - Widgets "
"is for UI components, not drawing"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/hardware/display.rst:48 a8375809be7541138ceeb8255902da80
msgid ""
"✅ **CORRECT**: ``from M5 import *; M5.Lcd.fillRect(...)`` - M5.Lcd "
"provides all drawing methods"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/hardware/display.rst:50 9f1c206de9e64327b2031bed1e42699d
msgid ""
"**Key Distinction**: - ``M5.Lcd`` = Drawing methods (fillRect, drawRect, "
"drawCircle, drawString, etc.) - ``M5.Widgets`` = UI component classes "
"(Label, Image, Rectangle, Circle, etc.)"
msgstr ""

